---
// The easy part. Quiet competence, reassurance not a sales pitch. Rendered as a
// calm navy depth band (the page's brand-neutral dark, shared with the hero and
// footer) so the light page gets rhythm. Requirements live here, framed as help.
---

<section class="easy section-y" id="why">
  <div class="container-x easy__content">
    <div class="easy__main reveal">
      <h2 class="t-h1 easy__title">We keep them ready. You just show up.</h2>
      <p class="easy__body">
        Because these are ours, they are always clean, fueled, and ready when you arrive. We meet you
        in person, walk you through everything so you start the day relaxed, and we are around if you
        need us. First time out or your hundredth, we set you up. The only thing you have to bring is
        the people you want to spend the day with.
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="easy__note reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 90ms">
      <p class="easy__note-label">A few simple things to rent</p>
      <p class="easy__note-text">
        A valid ID, the right age, and for boats a Florida boater safety card if you were born after
        1988. Not sure about any of it? Just ask. We are happy to point you to the right place.
      </p>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .easy {
    background-color: var(--color-ink);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  .easy__content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 1.5rem + 2.5vw, 3.5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .easy__title {
    color: var(--color-white);
    max-width: 16ch;
  }
  .easy__body {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
    max-width: 50ch;
  }
  .easy__note {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-sun);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: clamp(1.375rem, 1.1rem + 1.25vw, 2rem);
  }
  .easy__note-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-sun);
    margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
  }
  .easy__note-text {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
    max-width: 52ch;
  }
  /* A touch more separation between the statement and the requirements card
     when they stack on phones. */
  @media (max-width: 899px) {
    .easy__note {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .easy__content {
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
      gap: clamp(3rem, 2rem + 3vw, 5rem);
      align-items: center;
    }
    .easy__note {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
